overview: After being educated in England, Daisy Forbes returns to China, the country of her birth, and discovers that her father has recently died and that she has become a social outcast, owing to the public revelation that the oriental nurse who raised her was actually her mother...
tagline: All the allure of the Orient, with its seething Intrigues, its wily peoples, its mystery, and romance- are all found "East of Suez."
title: East of Suez
